CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774480286
OL,3,CGovernment will pause crypto donations
OL,4,Cto stop foreign interference in
OL,5,Celections
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIt will now be up to the Communities
OL,13,FSecretary Steve Reed and security
OL,14,Fminister Dan Jarvis, who chairs the
OL,15,Fgovernment's Defending Democracy
OL,16,FTaskforce, to review the report's
OL,17,Fseventeen recommendations and decide
OL,18,Fwhich will be accepted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774480286
OL,3,CGovernment will pause crypto donations
OL,4,Cto stop foreign interference in
OL,5,Celections
OL,7,FReed confirmed on Wednesday in the
OL,8,FCommons that restrictions on crypto
OL,9,Fdonations and caps on dual national
OL,10,Fdonations would be applied immediately.
OL,12,FThe remaining accepted recommendations
OL,13,Fwill be incorporated into the
OL,14,FRepresentation of the People Bill.
OL,16,FResponding to the review's
OL,17,Frecommendations, Shadow Housing and
OL,18,FCommunities Secretary Sir James
OL,19,FCleverly accused the government of
OL,20,Fenacting "policy by press release".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774480286
OL,3,CGovernment will pause crypto donations
OL,4,Cto stop foreign interference in
OL,5,Celections
OL,7,FHe went on to claim: "Labour's
OL,8,Fproposals on company donations will
OL,9,Fhave a significant domestic impact.
OL,10,FYet the Government have dodged proper
OL,11,Fconsultation and scrutiny of these
OL,12,Fplans.
OL,14,F"Ministers should tell us why they did
OL,15,Fnot wait for the Rycroft Review before
OL,16,Fintroducing this Bill. And if they are
OL,17,Freally serious about tackling foreign
OL,18,Finterference, they should put China on
OL,19,Fthe higher tier of the Foreign
OL,20,FInfluence Registration Scheme."
OL,26,@oD@VOUvD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
